# API catalog

Base: `{apiDomain}/api`. Response shape usually `{ success, data, error? }`. Banking list meta: `{ total, limit, offset, total_debit, total_credit, net_cashflow }`.

## Health / config

| Method | Path | File |
|--------|------|------|
| GET | `/health` | `server.js` |
| GET | `/config` | `routes/config.js` → ignorePlatforms |

## Investments — `routes/investments.js` + `db/*-store.js`

| Method | Path | Notes |
|--------|------|-------|
| GET | `/investments` | all |
| GET | `/investments/search?website_app_name&sub_type_name&sub_type_category` | |
| GET/PUT/DELETE | `/investments/:id` | |
| POST | `/investments` | body fields as domain model |

## Analytics — `routes/analytics.js`

MySQL path uses pool + `ignore-platform` + often `snapshot-queries`. Mongo → `utils/mongo-analytics.js`.

| GET path | Purpose |
|----------|---------|
| `/analytics/total` | sum + count |
| `/analytics/by-type` | group investment_type |
| `/analytics/by-month` / `by-year` | time buckets |
| `/analytics/monthly-changes` / `yearly-changes` | deltas |
| `/analytics/by-platform` | by website_app_name |
| `/analytics/growth` | growth series |
| `/analytics/value-series` | portfolio value over time (filters) |
| `/analytics/allocation-latest` | latest allocation |
| `/analytics/insights` | derived insights |
| `/analytics/delta?from&to` | period delta |
| `/analytics/cashflows-by-month` | investment_transactions |
| `/analytics/by-sub-type-name` / `by-sub-type-category` | |
| `/analytics/summary-table` | summary rows |
| `/analytics/investment-history/:id` | history |

## Categories — `routes/categories.js` + store

| Method | Path |
|--------|------|
| GET/POST | `/categories/sub-type-names` |
| GET | `/categories/sub-type-names/:investmentType` |
| DELETE | `/categories/sub-type-names/:id` |
| POST | `/categories/categories` |
| GET | `/categories/categories/:investmentType/:subTypeNameId?` |
| DELETE | `/categories/categories/:id` |
| POST | `/categories/sync-from-investments` | → `sync-lookup-tables.js` |

## Portfolio import/export — `routes/portfolio.js`

| Method | Path | Util |
|--------|------|------|
| GET | `/portfolio/export` | JSON investments |
| POST | `/portfolio/import` | upsert array via store |
| GET | `/portfolio/export/sql` | `sql-export.js` (Mongo→SQL too) |
| POST | `/portfolio/import/sql` | MySQL only; body `{ sql, freshInstall? }` |
| GET | `/portfolio/export/mongo` | `mongo-export.js` |
| POST | `/portfolio/import/mongo` | body `{ data, freshInstall? }` |

## Banking — `routes/banking.js` + `db/banking.js` + `banking-advanced.js`

| Area | Paths |
|------|-------|
| Accounts | CRUD `/banking/accounts`, `/banking/accounts/:id` |
| Continuity | GET `/banking/accounts/:id/continuity` |
| Txns | CRUD `/banking/transactions`; POST `bulk-categorize`, `bulk-delete` |
| Recat | POST `/banking/recategorize` |
| Categories | GET `/banking/categories` |
| Rules | CRUD `/banking/rules` |
| Analytics | GET `/banking/analytics` |
| Budgets | `/banking/budgets`, `/budgets/status`, DELETE `/budgets/:id` |
| Recurring | GET `/banking/recurring` |
| Transfers | POST `/banking/transfers/match` |
| Forecast | GET `/banking/forecast` |
| Import | POST `/banking/import` (multer file), `/import/preview`; DELETE `/import/batches/:batchId` |

Parsers: `utils/bank-parsers/index.js` — HDFC/ICICI/DCB/SBI/Axis/Kotak + generic; **no PDF**.
